<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Albrecht von Egloffstein zu Mühlhausen</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Rücknahme der Klage in weltlicher Sache gegen den Samuel von Schwarzach, Jude zu Nürnberg, vor dem geistlichen Gericht zu Bamberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_140" id="69v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_140_r2l1"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Albrechte<ex>n</ex></expan> von Eglofſtein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l2">cʒu Mülhauſen geſeſſen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_140_r2l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Albreht vns hat fürgelegt Sanvvel von Swarcʒach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l4"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Jude / vvie daʒ Jr vmb werltlich ſache auf <expan>geiſtlich<ex>e</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l6">gerihte cʒu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> v̈mbtreibt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_140_r2l5">beklagt </ab></add> / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vville<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l7">von der klag auf <expan>geiſtliche<ex>m</ex></expan> gerichte laſſen vvöllet / Als etc das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l8">wöllen etc / vnd het Jr <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu Jm icht <expan>cʒuſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Darümb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l9"> <expan>vvolle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jm </del> ew oder <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>ſcheinbote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gevvalt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l10"><expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> ſlewnigs <expan>reht<ex>en</ex></expan> etc <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_140" id="69v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Albrechte<ex>n</ex></expan> von Eglofstein, czu Mülhausen
                        gesessen</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Albreht, uns hat fürgelegt Sanwel von
                        Swarczach, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> jude, wie daz ir umb werltlich
                        sache auf <expan>geistlich<ex>e</ex>m</expan> gerihte czu
                                <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<add>beklagt</add>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> von der klag auf
                            <expan>geistliche<ex>m</ex></expan> gerichte lassen wöllet. Als etc. Das
                        wöllen etc. Und het ir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czu im icht <expan>czu
                                sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darümb <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        ew oder <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinbote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> slewnigs
                                <expan>reht<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.
                        <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
